Package eventorg

Class EventOrganizer

java.lang.Object
eventorg.EventOrganizer
public class EventOrganizer extends Object
User interface to process command line input for the Event Calendar. Can process a single or multiple lines at once.
Author:
Dany Chucri, Madhur Nutulapati
